citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
Section 2.126(b) - Access and inspection of records and property: A responsible adult shall be made available to
accompany APHIS officials during the inspection process.
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 5:05 pm on
03/16/2016.
Inspector arrived at facility at 5:05 pm and knocked on doors to house and called phone number and left message.
An individual who arrived at the facility stated that the licensee was not available for the inspection.
